## API Endpoints

### Public

```
POST /webhooks/clerk          Clerk webhook — user.created / user.deleted
```

### Protected (Clerk JWT required)

```
PATCH /users/me/push-token    Save Expo push token

POST  /dumps                  Submit text dump → split → queue jobs → return immediately
GET   /dumps                  List user's dumps

GET   /preps                  List user's preps (?status=prepping|ready|archived)
GET   /preps/:id              Single prep with full result + agent steps
PATCH /preps/:id/archive      User acted — archive

GET   /preps/:id/steps        Agent step log for this prep (for detail screen)

POST  /preps/:id/clarify      User replies to a clarify question → resumes job
```

